Brazil v Uruguay. 
Gary Lineker introduces live coverage of the first semi-final at the Fifa Confederations Cup in Brazil from Belo Horizonte's Estadio Mineirao. The winners of Group A, Brazil, take on Uruguay, the runners-up from Group B, for the right to play in Sunday's final at the iconic Estadio Maracana. Hosts Brazil are the defending champions and have won the tournament three times before. Commentary comes from Steve Wilson and Mark Lawrenson.
